snippet: The Olympic champion, Darya Domracheva of Belarus, won the women’s 15-kilometer individual race at the biathlon World Cup in Ostersund, Sweden.
abstract: Olympic champion Darya Domracheva of Belarus wins women's 15-kilometer individual race at the biathlon World Cup.
lead_paragraph: The Olympic champion, Darya Domracheva of Belarus, won the women’s 15-kilometer individual race at the biathlon World Cup in Ostersund, Sweden.

headline.main: Belarussian Wins World Cup Biathlon Race
